dct_title_s: Sketch Map illustrating the discovery of the Mouth of the Bembe, Limpopo, or Ouri River (South Africa) By St. Vincent W. Erskine
dct_description_sm: Published for the Journal of the Royal Geographical Society by J. Murray, Albemarle St. London 1869 ; Edwd. Weller.
Shows waterways, towns, roads, various place names, boundaries, Joachin de Santa Rita route, Mr. Erksine's route.
Journal of the Royal Geographic Society, volume 39, between pages 232-233.
